Step 7.   Delete the current MAGNUM relations in Schema CAIS.

          DIST.UUN, INTERNAL.UUNS

Step 8.   Run the MAGNUM program DIST.UUN.UPD to update the following
          relations:

          CUSTOMER, UUN.USR.NAM, DIST.UUN, INTERNAL.UUNS

